---
layout: base.njk
title: Reading list
description: The best writing on LIHTC, expiring affordability, and preservation. Curated, and growing.
permalink: /reading/
---
<header class="hero">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="eyebrow">Reading list</div>
    <h1>Everything worth reading on <span>LIHTC expiration</span>.</h1>
    <p class="deck">
      Nobody had made this list, so we made it. Reporting, research, and legislation —
      with a note on why each one matters.
    </p>
  </div>
</header>

<main class="section">
  <div class="container narrow">
    <div class="links">
      {% for item in links | reverse %}
      <div class="link">
        <div>
          <div class="from">{{ item.source }}</div>
          <h3><a href="{{ item.url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">{{ item.title }}</a></h3>
          <p class="why">{{ item.why }}</p>
        </div>
        <div class="yr">{{ item.year }}</div>
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>

    <div class="note" style="margin-top:36px">
      <b>Know something that belongs here?</b>
      This list is maintained by hand and it is definitely incomplete. Send it over and we'll add it.
    </div>
  </div>
</main>
